metadata.description: C4D, Octane, After Effects, & Code; A burning star warms the earth. Light gives way to darkness's birth. Sound design by @noisysavage.

attributes.value: Evan Pun is a Chinese, Vietnamese, and French 3D Artist & Designer based in San Francisco. He has worked as a multi-disciplinary designer for 8+years and has done a VFX for live shows and music videos. Grounded in storytelling Evan creates Cyberpunk, Sci-Fi, and anime-inspired worlds.
